程序包 daiwei.tojava.taskmanager

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Deadline
    This class extends from Object todo.
    Parser
    This Parser class is to parser full command and create todo, deadline tasks.
    Sort  
    Storage
    This class is to create load task from file Path and save task in file Path function.
    Task
    This class to create task object.
    TaskList
    This TaskList class to add Task,add deadline in TaskManager, and edit, delete the TaskManager.
    TaskManager
    This class implements simple task manager ,that can write, load and storage tasks in the assigned filePath.
    Todo
    This class extends from task object.
    Ui
    This class is to read user command and print error.
  • 异常错误概要 
    异常错误 说明
    TaskManagerException
